I"+<h2 style="font-family: Ergonomique Bold">Discrimination in STEM fields: Current racial and ethnic issues in the STEM work industry</h2>
<p>Caleb Izaguirre. 05/15/2021</p>
<hr />

<p>Race and gender disparities remain a significant challenge in STEM industries and the future of the American workforce. Among STEM workers, African Americans are centerpoint for concerns that there is too little attention paid to increasing racial and ethnic diversity; their high experience with issues with diversity in the workforce is constantly met with failure.</p>
